{"tid":1545850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺又一城間藍絲餐廳食到一肚火","createTime":"2019-09-06T05:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T12:27:05.000Z","uid":315957,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e6845a1112d83da3682aaafef229b956c9993a99","tid":1545850,"uid":315957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyBsaaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyBsaaR.jpg&h=c6198308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就5/8夜晚去食嘅<br />\n本身冇打算出聲<br />\n所以冇影相，張相上網搵嘅<br />\n但日日見到門口排長龍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 你地以後都吾好再去啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個晚食間垃圾聽到有佢地啲伙計話佢住個頭好似放<br />\n左tg想早收返去先。<br />\n<br />\n點知有個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白色西裝嬲嘅女人</span></span>(應該系大粒野)話佢吾理吾比收。<br />\n<br />\n又話系啲死暴徒搞到咁亂放tg系抵死，佢地要照做生意跑數<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手足你地唔系咁都食得落啊?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後咪撚再去食!<br />\n第一次嬲到出po<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"736553d0974067da17f5002a10140ee6174ff294","tid":1545850,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41e6d0a0049ebb7ddf7c91d7b6aab25395dc4f72","tid":1545850,"uid":149215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"［核彈]906全民太子站獻花，極重要！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href